.TH AUDIO_CONSUMER 1 "March 2026" "1.0.0" "ws-audiod"
.SH NAME
audio_consumer \- shared memory audio consumer for ws\-audiod
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B audio_consumer
.RI [ shm_name ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B audio_consumer
reads raw audio periods directly from the ws\-audiod shared memory region,
providing zero-copy access for real-time audio processing. Requires the daemon
to be running with \fBenable_sample_sharing=true\fR.
.SH ARGUMENTS
.TP
.I shm_name
Shared memory segment name (default: /ws_audiod_samples).
.SH AUTHOR
Ed Baker <ed@ebaker.me.uk>
